						Stk[Inst[2]] = #Stk[Inst[3]];
					elseif (Enum == 80) then
						Stk[Inst[2]][Stk[Inst[3]]] = Stk[Inst[4]];
					else
						VIP = Inst[3];
					end
				elseif (Enum <= 84) then
					if (Enum <= 82) then
						Upvalues[Inst[3]] = Stk[Inst[2]];
					elseif (Enum > 83) then
						do
							return;
						end
					else
						local A = Inst[2];
						local B = Stk[Inst[3]];
						Stk[A + 1] = B;
						Stk[A] = B[Inst[4]];
					end
				elseif (Enum <= 85) then
					for Idx = Inst[2], Inst[3] do
						Stk[Idx] = nil;
					end
				elseif (Enum == 86) then
					Stk[Inst[2]] = Stk[Inst[3]] - Stk[Inst[4]];
				else
					local A = Inst[2];
					Stk[A] = Stk[A](Stk[A + 1]);
				end
				VIP = VIP + 1;
			end
		end;
	end
	return Wrap(Deserialize(), {}, vmenv)(...);
end
